cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.RO 

This paper deals with action detection using computer vision techniques, specifically RGB and optical flow. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also proposes a new network architecture, which involves training and optimization, making cs.LG (Machine Learning) another likely category. The use of motion information and transformation parameters suggests the involvement of artificial intelligence techniques, making cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) another possible category. The paper also mentions experiments on datasets related to multimedia and robotics, indicating the involvement of cs.MM (Multimedia) and cs.RO (Robotics).
